est. Some are talkative, some are grumpy, but all of them will lend you an ear on your adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444300/extras/34330845a23c1bd37d4165e2480d79c1.poster.avif?t=1746799722\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444300/extras/34330845a23c1bd37d4165e2480d79c1.webm?t=1746799722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444300/extras/34330845a23c1bd37d4165e2480d79c1.mp4?t=1746799722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444300/extras/af270b31daa5af9401d663de7d87c8b8.webp?t=1746799722\" width=600 height=50 /></span><br>Most of the animals you meet will be glad to help Teacup… in exchange for a small favor or some help. Organize a (oddly shaped) market stall, win an underwater race and more!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444300/extras/c218866bcb4c9c38dfbb9e33bc30afb0.poster.avif?t=1746799722\" width=600 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444300/extras/c218866bcb4c9c38dfbb9e33bc30afb0.webm?t=1746799722\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1444300/extras/c218866bcb4c9c38dfbb9e33bc30afb0.mp4?t=1746799722\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
